{"tid":1369658,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"元朗天水圍屯門天主教堂明日全日加開宗教活動 ，歡迎任何有需要人士。","createTime":"2019-07-26T18:04:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T05:15:00.000Z","uid":222140,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"777a4d9e56fd4097f482d3d3580692e9eb41605a","tid":1369658,"uid":222140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T18:04:54.000Z","msg":"【天水圍  元朗  屯門 聖堂】<br />\n【2019.7.27週六開放情況】（7.27 -- 01:12更新聖葉理諾堂活動）<br />\n<br />\n（公教報訊）天水圍，元朗和屯門區聖堂七月廿七日（週六）除原有的提前主日彌撒外，其開放情況如下，附堂區連結：<br />\n＝＝天水圍聖葉理諾堂<br />\n27/7通宵開放至翌日<br />\n作祈禱/輔導/護理/休息之用<br />\n++下午3:00-5:30 祈禱之共融新力量<br />\n求聖神賜與我們力量為社會，教會及堂區的共融努力。<br />\n15:00 - 15:10 聖堂 410 集合<br />\n15:10 - 15:30 執事分享 （教會為何參與社會運動？DOCAT）<br />\n15:30 - 16:00 靈修入門<br />\n16:00 - 16:30 泰澤祈禱介紹及歌詠練習<br />\n16:30 - 17:30 泰澤祈禱<br />\n地址：天水圍天美街6號<br />\n電話：2448 8332<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/stjeromeschurch\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstjeromeschurch&d=vhywW4AIbf33TEOu71%2FwU%2Bf4PGxNkgPyFAzKtVao6pc%3D&h=e2c4173b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/stjeromeschurch</a><br />\n<br />\n＝＝聖伯多祿聖保祿堂（元朗）<br />\n27/7&mdash;&mdash;祈禱和反思日<br />\n上午8時：明供朝拜聖體（小聖堂）<br />\n下午3時： 慈悲時刻（大聖堂）<br />\n下午5時：彌撒（大聖堂 &ndash; 英語）<br />\n晚上6時30 分：彌撒（大聖堂 &ndash; 粵語）<br />\n由晚上8 時開始：祈禱和反思時間（大聖堂）<br />\n歡迎大家隨時來臨一起參與祈禱。<br />\n地址：新界元朗青山公路201號屏山段<br />\n電話：24760887<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/SSPETERANDPAUL.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FSSPETERANDPAUL.HK&d=vhywW4AIbf33TEOu71%2FwU%2Bf4PGxNkgPyFAzKtVao6pc%3D&h=285f7a56\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/SSPETERANDPAUL.HK</a><br />\n<br />\n＝＝屯門贖世主堂<br />\n27/7下午3時起明供聖體，為香港社會祈禱。<br />\n同時，亦會開放地方給有需要人士作休息之用。<br />\n地址：屯門鄉事會路二號<br />\n電話：2459 6510<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/holyredeemerchurchhk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fholyredeemerchurchhk&d=vhywW4AIbf33TEOu71%2FwU%2Bf4PGxNkgPyFAzKtVao6pc%3D&h=dcaafb1b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/holyredeemerchurchhk</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n教會幫到盡，全日有活動及祈禱會<br />\n元朗由昨晚開始已有通宵明供聖體儀式<br />\n有咩事解決唔到可以搵天主傾下"},{"pid":"e44b8b5dcde85d32c9b18338c4fe3cf9bea53c2e","tid":1369658,"uid":222140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T18:06:25.000Z","msg":"推推"},{"pid":"214280c3472467e435e2fd3f25955c08eb5130db","tid":1369658,"uid":166886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T18:08:32.000Z","msg":"左膠阿根廷神父<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58bf235266938703e866a7dc145406e23553c35b","tid":1369658,"uid":61191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T18:10:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"085b5ab9828b3f6e76d993b0c48a99de210579d8","tid":1369658,"uid":117005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T18:17:50.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"306840f12cfa0174b67fcf36fd1f0b9ec442fe19","tid":1369658,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T18:26:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1326f0f9106760c8620540fb7a02c431cf02048d","tid":1369658,"uid":167435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T18:38:28.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39dd71a91477a72008f764bc50ad433587835470","tid":1369658,"uid":222140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T05:04:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dcf6de303519ca79fd320c3222af3061fee74359","tid":1369658,"uid":48124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T05:12:56.000Z","msg":"We connect <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fa943a070c